  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0d9c\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0da0\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db4\u0dad\u0d9a\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dba\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The businessman who gave a valuable check was caught",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Panadura Special Crime Investigation Division says that a businessman who allegedly bought paint worth 14 lakhs 2065 rupees from a factory in Panadura North area and gave a valuable check was arrested.",
        "Police say that the suspect businessman residing in Dambulla area had obtained this ink in 2021.",
        "A police officer said that investigations were conducted based on a complaint made to the police by the manager of the Panadura factory that the bank informed him that there was no money in the account when he banked the check he had given.",
        "The police say that the suspected businessman was informed to come to the police on several occasions, but he avoided, so they went to the Dambulla area and arrested the suspect."
      ],
